  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      By performing a challenge with camel's milk in patients who are allergic to cow's milk, the
      investigators will examine if camel's milk is a safe alternative for these patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
